id: pm-oveq
title: SDK testing helper for registerFlags registrations
description: "Add a public SDK testing helper that lets package authors assert api.registerFlags(targetCommand, flags) registrations directly, export it from @unbrained/pm-cli/sdk and /sdk/testing, document the pattern, and cover it with focused tests. Duplicate check: pm search \"assertRegisteredFlags registerFlags testing helper\" found related closed helper items pm-aw7d, pm-kfd8, pm-01bm, pm-475h, pm-xevy and the command-kit exemplar pm-1js9, but no existing assertRegisteredFlags item or implementation."
type: Task
status: closed
priority: 2
tags[4]: agent-ux,"area:extensions","area:packages","area:sdk"
created_at: "2026-06-20T14:27:44.471Z"
updated_at: "2026-06-20T14:40:10.981Z"
author: codex-20260620
parent: pm-ugqx
resolution: Added and exported assertRegisteredFlags plus docs and regression coverage for package-author registerFlags assertions.
expected_result: Package authors can assert registerFlags registrations through the public SDK testing surface without private loader imports.
actual_result: "assertRegisteredFlags is available from both SDK entrypoints, validates target command and expected flag labels, returns the matching registration, and is documented/tested."
